      "content": "i hear you about the doctor but honestly i just want a clear plan i can follow at home. if i wanted to try this, how much garlic extract and spinach would i actually need to take daily to make sure my blood stays thin enough? like, is there a certain amount i should aim for to stay safe while i'm weaning off the warfarin?",
